Common packages for minimal Ubuntu server, stripped for Rockchip embedded.

 * feature: no-follow-recommends

== Core ==

 * apt
 * bzip2
 * ca-certificates
 * initramfs-tools
 * keyutils
 * krb5-locales
 * libpam-systemd
 * netbase
 * pollinate
 * snapd                   # required for snap-preseed
 * sudo
 * systemd
 * systemd-resolved
 * systemd-sysv
 * udev

== Block device / filesystem tools ==

 * e2fsprogs
